No. D-2482. In the Matter of Discipline of Jeffrey Thomas Kipi. 561 U.S. 1044, 131 S. Ct. 41,

177 L. Ed. 2d 1131,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 5566. July 26, 2010.

Jeffrey Thomas Kipi, of Oviedo, Florida, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court, and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
